a wave of terror
swept through Hoesan Village.

64
00:04:39,862 --> 00:04:42,949
Residents who gathered to see the scene,

65
00:04:43,032 --> 00:04:46,119
a site of brutal killings
with an on-site incinerator,

66
00:04:46,202 --> 00:04:49,914
trembled with disbelief
that such a thing could happen.

67
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:53,918
They committed such evil, atrocious acts.
Are they even human?

68
00:04:54,419 --> 00:04:55,295
Seriously,

69
00:04:56,587 --> 00:04:58,589
something needs to be done about them.

70
00:04:59,173 --> 00:05:02,802
They could've killed so many more
if they hadn't been stopped.

71
00:05:04,137 --> 00:05:06,014
My heart is still racing.

72
00:05:07,056 --> 00:05:09,267
Residents who knew the suspects

73
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:13,521
still look stunned
by the sheer brutality of their crimes.

74
00:05:13,604 --> 00:05:17,150
Even with all the rumors
going around town,

75
00:05:17,233 --> 00:05:19,485
I never imagined it would be this bad.

76
00:05:19,569 --> 00:05:21,904
We never caught on.

77
00:05:21,988 --> 00:05:26,701
And we had no idea
they were behind crimes like this.

78
00:05:28,369 --> 00:05:34,709
KANG DAE-OK, NEIGHBOR OF THE CHIJON FAMILY
AT THE TIME OF THE INCIDENT

79
00:05:36,544 --> 00:05:39,672
To be honest, it's all been forgotten now,

80
00:05:39,756 --> 00:05:42,925
but the stigma lingered for a long time
among outsiders.

81
00:05:43,009 --> 00:05:46,012
Even ten years ago,
people came to see where it happened.

82
00:05:46,095 --> 00:05:49,557
They'd come in tour buses and say,
"That's the Chijon place."

83
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:53,269
Seeing that made us feel
really uneasy and uncomfortable.

84
00:05:53,353 --> 00:05:54,979
So we'd just deny it.

85
00:05:55,063 --> 00:05:59,067
Basically, we covered it up
by saying it was a different house.

86
00:05:59,776 --> 00:06:01,277
That's the life we lived.

87
