They decided to take turns
giving them drinks.

137
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:22,853
"Let's just pretend to drink.
Don't actually drink any."

138
00:09:23,938 --> 00:09:25,940
LEE HYO-JIN
LAST SURVIVOR OF THE CHIJON FAMILY CASE

139
00:09:26,023 --> 00:09:29,652
"They need to be drunk
so they won't know where they're going."

140
00:09:29,735 --> 00:09:32,363
"So just tell them,
'You'll be home in the morning

141
00:09:32,446 --> 00:09:35,241
when you wake up,'
as you give them the drinks."

142
00:09:35,825 --> 00:09:41,455
So after getting the couple
completely drunk,

143
00:09:42,915 --> 00:09:48,045
they had the survivor come down
to the basement to carry out the crime.

144
00:09:48,129 --> 00:09:51,257
They put a shotgun in her hands
and told her, "Shoot them."

145
00:09:52,174 --> 00:09:53,426
"Only then

146
00:09:54,135 --> 00:09:55,219
can you become

147
00:09:55,928 --> 00:09:57,555
a true member of the gang."

148
00:09:57,638 --> 00:10:00,641
That's how they tried to convince her.

149
00:10:02,101 --> 00:10:07,732
I think it was too heavy
for me to hold with both hands.

150
