and dismembered them

171
00:12:00,261 --> 00:12:01,762
with knives and hatchets.

172
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,688
In a desperate,
life-threatening situation,

173
00:12:10,771 --> 00:12:13,566
the victim, a small business owner,
wrote a statement

174
