revealing the brutal nature
of the suspects' interrogation.

175
00:12:16,527 --> 00:12:20,030
Notes written by the perpetrators
were also found with it.

176
00:12:21,115 --> 00:12:23,701
Even as he feared death drawing closer,

177
00:12:23,784 --> 00:12:28,038
the victim begged the kidnappers
not to harm his wife and daughters.

178
00:12:28,539 --> 00:12:32,084
"I came from the streets too.
I know you're doing this to survive."

179
00:12:32,168 --> 00:12:34,211
He begged them,
"I can always earn more money,

180
00:12:34,295 --> 00:12:35,921
so I won't try anything funny,"

181
00:12:36,005 --> 00:12:38,382
but in the end, he was brutally murdered.

